title: Worker Contract
author: AgentMuu
pages:
#- By signing this contract I, the employer of the contracted worker swear to honor the agreements set forth and pay the Employee(s) the wage I have set, no more no less. I Acknowledge that the servies I request in this book are what I  shall
#- recieve. 

Signed,

-AgentMuu
Workers will grind to level 50 in any way they choose and enchant an item of the Employer's choosing. The Employer reserves the right to tip Workers at his discretion.
